<plot>Distraction is a story of two friends, Scott and Sal, who distract themselves from heartbreak and boredom in New York City. Scott is a single guy coping with a failed relationship and searching for a connection. Sal is his free-spirited buddy who thinks he knows just what Scott needs. What unfolds tests their friendship and their views on love.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?152221</url></doc>
